sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Seu codigo
    participant DB as Banco

    App->>DB: indexedDB.open(nome, versao)
    DB-->>App: onsuccess (conexao)

    App->>DB: db.transaction(store, modo)
    App->>DB: transaction.objectStore(store)
    App->>DB: store.add / put / get / delete
    DB-->>App: IDBRequest.onsuccess
    Note over App: Resultado em event.target.result
